/* Transliteration seed: sml/parser/parser.sml — assignBinop (lines ~371–381).
   Stand-in token band 211–220 (PLUSEQ … GTGTEQ) until lexer/token_op_core lists compound assigns.
   Return value matches Ast binop order: Add=1 … Shr=10 (numeric ids for tests, not full AST). */

